OL,3,CWoman fears loss of inheritance after
OL,4,Claw firm's sudden collapse
OL,6,FA woman who was using a collapsed law
OL,7,Ffirm for probate says she fears the
OL,8,Finheritance left by her parents has
OL,9,Fbeen "lost".
OL,11,FKathryn Hobson, from Sheffield, is one
OL,12,Fof hundreds of clients left in limbo
OL,13,Fafter PM Law, which is based in the
OL,14,Fcity, closed suddenly on 2 February.
OL,16,FThe Solicitors Regulation Authority is
OL,17,Finvestigating potential fraud,
OL,18,Fincluding the misappropriation of
OL,19,Fcustomers' money.
