OL,3,CWoman fears loss of inheritance after
OL,4,Claw firm's sudden collapse
OL,6,FMs Hobson said it was "upsetting and
OL,7,Fdistressing" that her inheritance was
OL,8,Fstill inaccessible 11 months after the
OL,9,Fdeath of her mother Audrey Hardy.
OL,11,FShe said their case was days from
OL,12,Fbeing settled, but added: "There's
OL,13,Fstill no update or confirmation of
OL,14,Fwhat's really happening - we're still
OL,15,Fno further forward. We're in no-man's
OL,16,Fland, just waiting again.
OL,18,F"It's mum and dad's life savings, and
OL,19,Fsolicitors are the very people you
OL,20,Ftrust more than any other sector
OL,21,Freally.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/8
