OL,3,CWoman fears loss of inheritance after
OL,4,Claw firm's sudden collapse
OL,6,F"(My parents) would be furious and
OL,7,Fupset - and we're hoping this money is
OL,8,Fsafe, but we still don't even know
OL,9,Fthat yet. We don't know if the money
OL,10,Fis lost, it's just heartbreaking.
OL,12,F"One day you feel angry, the next you
OL,13,Fwant to break down. We're literally
OL,14,Fpowerless."
OL,16,F'It's been so stressful'
OL,18,FParents Rachael and Mark Brown were
OL,19,Fabout to move house from Leeds to
OL,20,FNorth Lincolnshire as they expect
OL,21,Ftheir third child.
