OL,3,CWoman fears loss of inheritance after
OL,4,Claw firm's sudden collapse
OL,6,FThey were using a conveyancing firm
OL,7,Fowned by PM Law before its collapse,
OL,8,Fleaving them #1,100 out of pocket.
OL,10,FRachael said: "It's been so stressful
OL,11,Ffor us, we don't know where we stand.
OL,13,F"We thought it would be a
OL,14,Fstraightforward and it's not been at
OL,15,Fall.
OL,17,F"We're back to square one in terms of
OL,18,Four sale so we don't know when we're
OL,19,Fgoing to be moving."
