OL,4,Claw firm's sudden collapse
OL,6,FMark added: "We wanted to get
OL,7,Feverything done as quick as we could -
OL,8,Fwe've been trying to rush it through,
OL,9,Feven dropping the price of the house
OL,10,Fto try and get it sold quickly.
OL,12,F"And then, suddenly, you get gazumped
OL,13,Fby something like this, and you think
OL,14,Fthings are going to take a lot longer
OL,15,Fthan planned."
OL,17,F'We're just sitting here waiting'
