OL,3,CWoman fears loss of inheritance after
OL,4,Claw firm's sudden collapse
OL,6,FRoydyn Evans was left with permanent
OL,7,Fnerve damage and unable to work after
OL,8,Fa road accident in 2024 that was not
OL,9,Fhis fault.
OL,11,FHe had just managed to prove his
OL,12,Finjuries were a result of the crash
OL,13,Fand was using PM Law to claim
OL,14,Fcompensation.
OL,16,FJust as Roydyn was about to receive a
OL,17,Fsettlement, his case was put on hold.
OL,19,FHe said: "We're just sitting here
OL,20,Fwaiting for what can happen next.
