OL,6,F"PM Law have done 99.9% of my case and
OL,7,Fif I go and find another solicitor,
OL,8,Fthey're going to take over a case
OL,9,Fthat's virtually ready to present and
OL,10,Fthey are going to make a fortune out
OL,11,Fof me for very little work."
OL,13,FOn Thursday the national fraud
OL,14,Freporting service Report Fraud said it
OL,15,Fwas "aware of allegations of fraud
OL,16,Fcommitted in relation to the
OL,17,Funexpected closure of PM Law Ltd
OL,18,Fgroup".
